 Industrial Production Localization # RailTech helps international manufacturers adapt and localize their products for the Uzbekistan market, ensuring full compliance with local regulatory requirements.
What Localization Includes # Regulatory Adaptation — aligning products and documentation with Uzbekistan requirements Certification — obtaining necessary certificates and permits for operation in the country Assembly Organization — establishing local production facilities for component assembly Technology Transfer — transferring knowledge and technology for equipment support and maintenance Ready to discuss your project? Contact us for a commercial proposal or browse the B2B catalog to find the right equipment.
